{"tid":2406953,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"蘋果： 「相達生物科技」無經市民同意拎左佢地口水做快速測試 測試結果仲做埋宣傳推廣","createTime":"2021-02-13T15:08:30.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-13T16:13:57.000Z","uid":22556,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"9b59de5cfb2fea78080faa465b7e877ae7cda0b1","tid":2406953,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-13T15:08:30.000Z","msg":"政府各社區檢測點為市民採樣後，會用作進行「核酸檢測」。惟《蘋果》揭發，政府檢測承辦商之一「相達生物科技國際有限公司」，竟在未有知會及獲市民同意下，將樣本同時用作進行另一款「快速抗原測試」，而本報進一步調查更發現，民政總署在本月初更曾主動向市民派發該公司的抗原測試套裝。<br />\n<br />\n【相達擅取市民樣本測試宣傳檢測包　曾獲民政總署協助向市民派發】<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/3jMFqBM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F3jMFqBM&d=kdQtjCisvz5VKkzPdH2zQ%2BL6SC4MthnAeNENlMyEb%2BY%3D&h=41a619eb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/3jMFqBM</a><br />\n<br />\n今日A1頭條：<br />\n【暗做兩款驗毒　數據用作宣傳產品　官方檢測公司呃市民做白老鼠】<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2MTpnGs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2MTpnGs&d=kdQtjCisvz5VKkzPdH2zQ%2BL6SC4MthnAeNENlMyEb%2BY%3D&h=6a134aec\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2MTpnGs</a><br />\n【驗逾九千樣本　相達最少袋230萬】<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2NmiUU6\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2NmiUU6&d=kdQtjCisvz5VKkzPdH2zQ%2BL6SC4MthnAeNENlMyEb%2BY%3D&h=c7059683\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2NmiUU6</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/105259197447/posts/10159878165752448/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F105259197447%2Fposts%2F10159878165752448%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=kdQtjCisvz5VKkzPdH2zQ%2BL6SC4MthnAeNENlMyEb%2BY%3D&h=50cfc135\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/105259197447/posts/10159878165752448/?d=n</a>"},{"pid":"5ab9c68b33c97ea5f33fbdab95942d53677c947b","tid":2406953,"uid":89182,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-13T15:11:25.000Z","msg":"DNA比曬中共了<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" clas